Text: I can't understand why your all stuck on 98.8%. According to bit torrent I only have 99.6% of the file, which is bollocks, because I uploaded it and nothing has changed in the folder since I did. Anyone know how to fix this?
Thanks for the music. The problem was two rogue files duplicating track 16 but with .sfa file extensions. They were possibly associated with video content. Simply delete them & voila!
